{"tid":1852834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"戒丁前後對比圖，戒丁脫毒","createTime":"2020-01-30T15:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T19:37:45.000Z","uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a769e5ff406f159515c19741d4232781cdbb500","tid":1852834,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"《 對比圖 》<br />\n<a href=\"http://noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnoj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D63&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=19e0fd32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=20ec01ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=af0fc2f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE戒色圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA%2Fvideos&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=bd9d0955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA/videos</a><br />\n<br />\n香港戒色論壇<br />\n<a href=\"http://noj1314.258club.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnoj1314.258club.com&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=e886a372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://noj1314.258club.com</a><br />\n<br />\n秦東魁老師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLyVAEphpUDM&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=42fa21ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM</a><br />\n<br />\n戒色吧<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%BD%E4%C9%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Ff%3Fkw%3D%25BD%25E4%25C9%25AB&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=4793dc6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%BD%E4%C9%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知：<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞<br />\n但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"071a01adca257ffc8a65133181b0c746087a95f9","tid":1852834,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"打Ｊ既你冇資格擁有愛情，所有打丁的人，都有一個共同特點，就是長相猥瑣，精神萎靡頹廢，行尸走肉。精氣神，精沒有了，陽氣、正氣就沒有了，神就沒有了！男人可以不帥，但一定要有精氣神！腎為先天之本，腎虛則百病叢生。打Ｊ會令你出現好多症狀，但係溝女方面，有三點對溝女方面有致命影響。 <br />\n<br />\n第一：打Ｊ會令你變樣衰，猥瑣，冇陽氣、正氣，雙眼無神，臉色晦暗無光澤 <br />\n第二：社交恐懼症，自卑冇自信，害羞內向，不敢正視異性，冇勇氣去主動 <br />\n第三：記憶力、注意力、思考力、理解力都會下降，反應遲鈍，諗唔到話題 <br />\n<br />\n以上症狀只要通過戒色，會慢慢恢復好。只要你戒Ｊ，你就會慢慢變返靚仔，自信，到時見到岩既女仔就敢主動去追！對於一個堅持戒色的人來說，你不要擔心找不到女朋友，你越堅持的越久，你能找到女朋友的起點越高，也越會有女人緣，一個內心陽光，滿身正氣的男人絕對不差機會。人，心淨了，身體就乾淨了，身體乾淨了女孩就來了。每一個戒色之人，請不必著急只需努力戒色努力進步，一切事情自然水到渠成。戒J吧，告別頹廢，戒出精彩人生！"},{"pid":"6d4521727664149ede61d60014216f7c3d686b13","tid":1852834,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a502c3936e18415d79b0ce368b4d0cc54919b13f","tid":1852834,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d379f7daff1b55d50ed1b521d8fc00c5dbdfb75d","tid":1852834,"uid":162095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"Wucfu 話精氣神好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比啲掙扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee70c643b861714ef74cf720214fd17f2e926b6","tid":1852834,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"有冇tg group"},{"pid":"6763f59f32b53fec92b2499781867592e8d27248","tid":1852834,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aee70c643b861714ef74cf720214fd17f2e926b6","tid":1852834,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:58:16.000Z","msg":"有冇tg group"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=20ec01ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a>"},{"pid":"8f5d5af5